msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:95 f4077bec6dec4c979d4fca6239cc772c
msgid ""
"Now you can test by locking the screen with ``ctrl`` + ``alt`` + ``l`` . "
"If it was successful and you are pleased with the results, restart your "
"computer."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:97 482351e08b3d48ddad3dbf6daecadb31
msgid ""
"**Note**: When logging in. the first thing you put is the TOTP secret and"
" then the password. This is true in the screen locker and as well as the "
"session manager (the login window that shows right after you put the disk"
" encryption passphrase)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:99 46a80907e2df450fb3d3a34650646d65
