#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:211 4010badac12a426099f75c177b0285f7
msgid "Configure your YubiKey / NitroKey3:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:215 bdb80abbecf546ecaab0600dfb82d9bb
msgid ""
"Configure your YubiKey for challenge-response ``HMAC-SHA1`` mode. This "
"can be done on any qube, e.g. a disposable (you need to :doc:`attach the "
"YubiKey </user/how-to-guides/how-to-use-usb-devices>` to this app qube "
"though) or directly on the sys-usb vm. You need to (temporarily) install "
"the package “yubikey-personalization-gui” and run it by typing ``yubikey-"
"personalization-gui`` in the command line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:217 580cfb4e392e46769b36bd7cc17f1a98
msgid "In the program go to ``Challenge-Response``,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:219 6c63def144a145d9a3851a712d5e652d
msgid "select ``HMAC-SHA1``,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:221 87756f825486459db16c1625669ce1bc
msgid "choose ``Configuration Slot 2``,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/security-in-qubes/mfa.rst:223 cbb242e259f64b6e968ffb5b8cce6e79
